throw out a good product or an item to pull in more customers - then throw out another good product to keep them happy and to bring more.

Can someone post Ella set #190? That's the old FF series. Thanks!

Time will tell if Virginia's last set was a turning point, or a lone tease followed by more dept store poses. Looks like someone at FG's trying to prolong the mystery, but I think they're just losing the interest of the majority. To be fair, these 3 will always have a fan base, but that won't mean much if they can't get more paying members interested. Too much out there to play puritan forever; fans will eventually go elsewhere...
As always WMI, thx for your hard work, it is appreciated...
